Gets stats from http://myservices.relianceada.com/ and shows the
bandwitch usage, dividing it in based on 'peak' and 'off peak' usage. 

You have to replace YOUR_PHONE_NO with your phone no.

Its a small hack, and solves my purpose. I am not interested in
bringing up lots of statistics etc around this.

By the way, there are bugs also (and you thought its a free
lunch?). Ex: it wont work around year starting etc.
